TITLE: Exchange lines and chars
PRIO: 1
STATUS: coding
FILES: mykeys.e
UPDATED: $Id: format001,v 1.1 2002-07-17 15:56:15 cla Exp $

Alt+Sh+<arrow key> will exchange lines down/up or chars left/right.                           

Hint:
- may conflict with PageMage keys, must be selectable !
